message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product, which I believe would significantly benefit your business. Given its high value to you, I propose an offer of $9500 for the product. This price reflects its exceptional quality and the potential return on investment it promises. I understand that negotiations are part of the process, so if this offer aligns with your expectations, please let me know. Should you require more information or have any questions, I am here to assist you. Looking forward to your positive response.
